nodes.text: This male was part of the Mandalorian Death Watch during the Clone Wars.
Around 21 BBY, he and other Death Watch Mandalorians guarded the Death Watch hideout on the moon Concordia.
He was later present with Death Watch commander Pre Vizsla when Vizsla and Dooku planned the take over of Mandalore.
The Death Watch trooper was voiced by Stephen Stanton, who also provided the voice for Mas Amedda in the same episode.
